{
  "texts": [
    "It was reported that the engineers asked the chatbot to search for errors in the source code of a database and create session logs, among other things.",
    "Following these incidents, Samsung restricted the length of employees' ChatGPT prompts and began developing its own internal chatbot.",
    "ChatGPT's privacy policy indicates that data is used for model training unless users explicitly choose an opt-out option.",
    "It is recommended not to share sensitive information via chatbots in general, as this data may not be deleted from the system.",
    "A study has revealed that it is possible to extract training data from diffusion models 43, which concerns the security and protection of data processed in AI systems."
  ]
}